\id GAL Meitei: Roman Script 1st Translation
\h Galatians
\toc1 GALATIA-GI Misingda I-ba Paul-gi Chithi
\toc2 Galatia
\toc3 Gal
\mt1 GALATIA-GI
\mt2 Misingda I-ba Paul-gi Chithi
\imt1 Wahoudok
\ip Jisugi Aphaba Paona Jihudi nattaba misingda sandokpa hourabada amadi makhoina lousillabada, asengba christian ama oinabagidamak Moses-ki Wayel Yathang adu ingadra nattraga illoidabra haiba wahang ama thoraklammi. Paul-na madu mathou tade haina yetli madudi tasengna hairabada, Christtada hingba punsi amagidamak amata ngairaba yumpham adudi madugi mapanna mi pumnamakpu Tengban Mapugi mangda chumhanbiriba thajaba aduni. Adubu Asia Minor-da leiba Rome leingakki lam Galatia-da leiba singlupsinggi marakta Tengban Mapugi mangda chumhanbinaba Moses-ki Wayel Yathang adusu thajaba amana ngakkadabani haina haiba Paul-gi maiyokta leppa mising thoraklammi.
\ip Paul-na AD. 48-49 aduwaida Galatia-gi misingda ikhiba chithi asi asigumba lanna tambiba asina lanna lamjingbikhraba mising adubu asengba thajaba amadi chatnabising aduda amuk hanna puraknabagidamak ikhibani. Jisu Christtagi pakhonchatpa ama koubagi mahakki hak adugi maramda palladuna chithi asi hou-i. Mahakpu pakhonchatpa ama oina koubiba adu karigumba mioibagi matik amatadagi natte adubu Tengban Mapudagini haiba aduga mahakki thougal adu akhannana Jihudi nattabasinggi maraktani haina mahakna kanna hai. Adudagi mahakna thajabakhaktagi mapanna misingbu Tengban Mapugi mangda chumhanbi haiduna yetnaba adu sengdok-i. Aroiba pandupsingda Christtabu thajabadagi mahei oiriba nungsiba adudagi Christian-singgi machat adu mahousana thokcharak-i haibadu Paul-na utli.
\iot Yaopham Takpa
\io1 1. Wahoudok \ior (1:1-10)\ior*
\io1 2. Pakhonchatpa ama oina Paul-gi matik \ior (1:11–2:21)\ior*
\io1 3. Tengban Mapugi thoujalgi aphaba pao \ior (3:1–4:31)\ior*
\io1 4. Christian-gi ningtamba amasung toupham thokpa thoudang \ior (5:1–6:10)\ior*
\io1 5. Waroisin \ior (6:11-18)\ior*
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Misingdagi nattaba aduga misinggi mapandagisu nattaba, adubu Jisu Christta amadi Ibungobu asibadagi hinggat-hanbiba Mapa Ibungo Tengban Mapugi mapandagi pakhonchatpa ama oina koubiraba Paul eina,
\v 2 Aduga eiga mapham asida loinariba thajaba ichil-inao pumnamakna khurumjabagi wahei asi Galatia-da leiriba singlupsingda thajari.
\p 
\v 3 Ipa Ibungo Tengban Mapu amadi Ibungo Jisu Christtana nakhoida thoujal amadi ingthaba pinabiba oisanu.
\p 
\v 4 Eikhoibu houjikki phattraba chak asidagi kanbinaba eikhoigi Tengban Mapu amadi Ipa adugi aningba adubu injaduna eikhoigi papkidamak Christtana masamakpu katthokpire.
\v 5 Lomba naida naidana Tengban Mapuda matik mangal oisanu. Amen!
\s1 Aphaba Pao asi nattaba atei amata leite
\p 
\v 6 Christtagi thoujalda hingnanaba nakhoibu koubiba mahakpu asuk thuna thadoktuna tonganba aphaba pao amada nakhoina onsinkhiba asida ei ngak-i.
\v 7 Asengbamak “Atoppa aphaba pao” ama leite, adubu nakhoibu pukning olhanba amasung Christtagi Aphaba Pao adubu hongdoknaba hotnaba mi khara leibagi maramna eina masi haibani.
\v 8 Adubu eikhoimakna nattraga swargadagi dut amana eikhoina nakhoida sandokkhiba aphaba pao adu nattaba tonganba aphaba pao ama sandoklabadi mahak norokta tasanu.
\v 9 Eikhoina masi hannasu haikhre, aduga houjik amukkasu hanna hairi: Nakhoina lousinkhraba Aphaba pao adu nattaba tonganba Aphaba Pao ama nakhoida kanagumbana sandoklabadi, mahak norokta tasanu.
\p 
\v 10 Houjik eina misingna yanaba hotnaribra nattraga Tengban Mapuna yanaba hotnaribra? Nattraga eina misingbu pelhannaba hotnaribra? Karigumba eina houjikphaoba misingbu pelhannaba hotnaramlabadi, eina Christtagi manai oiramloidabani.
\s1 Paul-bu Tengban Mapuna koubiba
\p 
\v 11 Ichil-inaosa, eina sandokkhiba aphaba pao asi mioibadagi lakpa natte haibasi eina nakhoida khanghanjaning-i.
\v 12 Masi eina mi kanadagisu phangkhiba natte aduga kananasu eingonda tambikhiba natte. Adubu Jisu Christta masamakna masi eingonda phongdokpibani.
\p 
\v 13 \x - \xo 1:13 \xt Pakhon 8:3; 22:4,5; 26:9-11\x*Eina Jihudigi laining laisonda lupcharingei matamda eina karamna hinglamba, eina Tengban Mapugi singluppu karamna minungsi yaodana ot-neiramba aduga madubu manghannaba angamba thakta hotnaramba adu nakhoina takhre.
\v 14 \x - \xo 1:14 \xt Pakhon 22:3\x*Jihudi laining lichatta eina atoppa lengmannaba Jihudi kayadagi mang tharammi amasung eikhoigi ipa-ipugi chatnabisingda kayada henna thawai yaojarammi.
\p 
\v 15 \x - \xo 1:15,16\xt Pakhon 9:3-6; 22:6-10; 26:13-18\x*Adubu eina imagi pibuknungda leiringeidagi mahakki thoujalna Tengban Mapuna eihakpu mahakki thougal tounaba koubire. Amasung mahakna wa lepkhrabada,
\v 16 haibadi mahakki Aphaba Pao adubu atoppa phurupsingda sandoknabagidamak Machanupa adubu iphamda phongdoknaba lepkhrabada, eina mi kanagi maphamdasu wa tannanaba chatkhide.
\v 17 Aduga eigi mangda pakhonchatpa oirambasing adubu unanaba Jerusalem-dasu chatkhide. Madugi mahutta eina khudak aduda Arabia-da chatlammi aduga adudagi eina Damascus-ta halakkhi.
\v 18 \x - \xo 1:18 \xt Pakhon 9:26-30\x*Adudagi eina chahi ahum leiraba matungda, Peter-dagi pao phangnabagidamak Jerusalem-da chatlammi amasung mahakka loinana numit taramangani leiminnarammi.
\v 19 Aduga eina Ibungogi manao Jacob nattana atei pakhonchatpa kana amatabu ukhide.
\p 
\v 20 Eina iriba asi achumbani. Eina minamba ngangde haiba Tengban Mapuna khang-i!
\p 
\v 21 Madugi matungda eina Syria amadi Cilicia-gi maphamsingda chatlammi.
\v 22 Matam aduda Christtada leiba Judea-gi singlupki misingna eibu hakthengnana sakkhanglamde.
\v 23 Makhoina khangba haibabu “Eikhoibu mamangda ot-neiramba nupa asina mahakna matam amada mang-hannanaba hotnaramba thajaba adu houjik sandokli” haina misingna hainaba adu khaktani.
\v 24 Aduga makhoina eigi maramgidamak Tengban Mapubu thagatcharammi.
\c 2
\s1 Paul-bu atoppa Pakhonchatpasingna lousinjaba
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 2:1 \xt Pakhon 11:30; 15:2\x* Chahi taramarigi matungda eina Barnabas-ka loinana Titus-pu puraduna Jerusalem-da amuk chatlammi.
\v 2 Madu Tengban Mapuna eingonda chatlu haina phongdokpibagi maramna chatpani. Aduga luchingbasing aduga lanai tonganna unaduna eina atoppa phurupsingda sandokpa aphaba pao adugi maramda makhoida sandokna tamle. Madu eina houkhibada toukhiba amadi houjik touriba thabaksing adu arembada tahanba pamdabagini.
\v 3 Aduga, eigi mapang oiriba Titus-na Greek macha oidunasu mangonda un kaknanaba namlamde.
\v 4 Adubu makhoi kharanadi madu pangthok-hanba pamkhi. Christta Jisuga amata oiminnabagi mapanna eikhoida leiriba ningtamba adu khangdoknabagidamak mising asina thajaba mi sasinnaduna lonna lanjaba amagum eikhoigi irakta changlakkhi. Makhoina eikhoibu minai oihanba pamkhi.
\v 5 Adubu Aphaba Paogi achumba adu nakhoigidamak mang-handana thamnabagidamak makhoida eikhoina mikup ama phaoba pikhide.
\p 
\v 6 \x - \xo 2:6 \xt Aniwa 10:17\x*Aduga maruoiba luchingbasingni haina lounariba makhoising adugi oinadi, (eina masi haibagi maramdi makhoina kari kari oirabasu eingonda karisu khetnaba leihande; Tengban Mapudi mapanthonggi oiba aduna wayende), eina sandokliba pao aduda makhoina karisu hapchinningai leikhide.
\v 7 Madugi onnabada, Jihudisingda aphaba pao sandoknabagidamak Tengban Mapuna Peter-da thoudang pinabibagum Jihudi nattaba phurupsingda aphaba pao sandoknaba Tengban Mapuna iphamda thoudang pinabiba adu makhoina ukhi.
\v 8 Maramdi Peter-bu Jihudisinggidamak pakhonchatpa oihanbikhiba adugumna Tengban Mapugi panggalna eihakpusu atoppa phurupsinggidamak pakhonchatpa oihanbire.
\v 9 Tengban Mapuna akhannaba thabak asi eingonda pinabire haina singlupki yumbini haina ikaikhumnariba Jacob, Peter amadi John-na khanglabada eikhoi pumnamak thougal touminnabasingni haibagi khudam oina Barnabas amadi eigi khut sokpire. Aduga Barnabas amasung eina Jihudi nattaba phurupsingda aduga makhoina Jihudisingda thougal touba haina eikhoina yanakhi.
\v 10 Amasung makhoigi marakta leiriba laira-anangsingbu eikhoina ningsingbiyu haina makhoina hairammi. Masimak eina touningbana ikhoulangliba thabak adumakni.
\s1 Paul-na Peter-bu Antioch-ta cheiba
\p 
\v 11 Adubu Peter-na Antioch-ta lakpa matamda, miyam mangda eina mahakki maiyokta lepkhi. Maramdi mahak sengna lallammi.
\v 12 Maramdi Jacob-na tharakpa mising aduna mapham aduda thungladringei mamangda Peter-na Jihudi nattaba atoppa phurupki thajabasing aduga chamin-thakminnarammi. Adubu makhoina thunglarabada mahakna Jihudi nattabasing adudagi lapthoraklammi amasung chamin-thaminnaramde, maramdi makhoibu un kakpa pamba makhoising adubu mahakna kirammi.
\v 13 Aduga atoppa Jihudigi maraktagi thajabasing adunasu Peter-gi pangdaba matou adugumna touba houraklammi. Madudi makhoigi pangdaba matou aduna Barnabas phaoba lanna lamjinglammi.
\v 14 Makhoina Aphaba Pao adugi achumba adugi matung-inna chumna chattre haiba urabada, makhoi pumnamakki mamangda eina Peter-da haikhi, “Nahak Jihudi amani, adumakpu nahakna Jihudi amagumna nattaduna atoppa phurupki mi amagi matougum hingli. Adu oiragadi kamdouna nahakna atoppa phurupki misingda Jihudigi chatnabising adu illu haina namlibano?”
\s1 Thajabagi mapanna Jihudi amadi Jihudi nattabasingbu kanbiba
\p 
\v 15 Eikhoidi pokpadagi Jihudisingni, aduga atoppa phurupsinggumna papchenbasing natte.
\v 16 \x - \xo 2:16\xt Isei 143:2; Rom 3:20; 3:22\x*Adumakpu mi amabu wayel yathanggi thabakki mapanna keidounungda Tengban Mapugi mangda chumhanbiba natte adubu Jisu Christtada thajabakhaktagi mapanna chumhanbibani haiba adu eikhoi khang-i. Maram aduna eikhoinasu, wayel yathanggi thabakki mapanna nattana Christtada thajabagi mapanna eikhoibu Tengban Mapugi mangda chumhanbinanaba Christta Jisuda eikhoina thajare. Maramdi wayel yathanggi thabakki mapanna mi kana amatabu chumhanbide.
\v 17 Adubu eikhoina Christtagi mapanna Tengban Mapugi mangda chumhanbinaba thibada, eikhoibu atoppa phurupsinggumna papchenba oina phanglabadi pap touhannabagidamak Christtana thougal tou-i hairibra? Madu suknat natte.
\v 18 Eina thugaikhraba wayel yathanggi pathap adubu eina amuk hanna sagatlabadi eihak wayel yathang thugaiba amani haiba isana utchabani.
\v 19 Maramdi eina Tengban Mapugidamak hingjanaba eina wayel yathanggi mapanna wayel yathangda sire.
\v 20 Eina Christtaga loinana cross-ta siminnare aduga hingliba asi ei natte, adubu Christtana eingonda hingbibani. Eina houjik hingjariba punsi asi eibu nungsibiriba amadi eihakkidamak masagi punsi katthokpikhraba Tengban Mapugi Machanupa adu thajabagi mapannani.
\v 21 Tengban Mapugi thoujal adu eina kakthatpa toude. Maramdi wayel yathanggi mapanna mi amabu Tengban Mapugi mangda chumhanbiba oiramlabadi, Christtana sibiba adu aremba oihalle.
\c 3
\s1 Wayel yathang amasung thajaba
\p 
\v 1 Ho apangba Galatia-gi misa! Kanana nakhoibu sumkhrabage? Jisu Christtana cross-ta sibikhiba adu nakhoigi mitmangda thokkhibagum madugi wahanthok adu nakhoida sandokna haikhre.
\v 2 Eina nakhoidagi wa amakhak khangba pammi: Nakhoina Tengban Mapugi Thawai adu wayel yathanggi thabakki mapanna phanglibra nattraga nakhoina takhraba Aphaba pao adu thajabagi mapanna phanglibra?
\v 3 Nakhoina karigi aduk yamna panglibano? Nakhoina Thawaigi mapanna houkhraga houjik nakhoina hakchanggi mapanna loisinnaba hotnaribra?
\v 4 Nakhoina arembada asuk yamna awaba khanglabra? Tasengnamak madu aremba oirabra?
\v 5 Tengban Mapuna nakhoida wayel yathanggi thabakki mapanna Thawai adu pibra amadi angakpa thabaksing toubra nattraga nakhoina takhraba Aphaba Pao adu thajabagi mapannara?
\p 
\v 6 \x - \xo 3:6 \xt Meihou 15:6; Rom 4:3\x*Abraham-na thengnakhiba adu nakhoina wakhal tou; Mapugi Puyada haikhibagumna, “Mahakna Tengban Mapubu thajakhi aduga mahakki thajaba adugi mapanna Tengban Mapuna mahakpu achumba chatpa ama oina singthanabikhi.”
\v 7 \x - \xo 3:7 \xt Rom 4:16\x*Adu oirabadi thajaba leiba makhoising adu Abraham-gi asengba chada-naodasingni haiba nakhoina khanggadabani.
\v 8 \x - \xo 3:8 \xt Meihou 12:3\x*Atoppa phurupsingbu thajabagi mapanna Tengban Mapuna chumhanbigani haina Mapugi Puyada mangjounana phongdokpikhre. Aduga asumna Mapugi Puyana Abraham-da Aphaba Pao asi laothokle, “Nahakki napanna Tengban Mapuna mi pumnamakpu yaipha thoujal phangjagani.”
\v 9 Abraham-na thajakhi amasung yaipha thoujal phangjakhi; aduga asumna thajaraba makhoi pumnamakna Abraham-na oikhibagumna yaipha thoujal phangjagani.
\p 
\v 10 \x - \xo 3:10 \xt Aniwa 27:26\x*Wayel yathang ngakchabada tangjariba makhoising adu sirapki makhada hinglibani. Maramdi Mapugi Puyada asumna iduna lei, “Wayel Yathanggi lairikta iriba khudingmakpu matam pumnamakta ngakpa ngamdaba mi khudingmak Tengban Mapugi sirap phanglabani.”
\v 11 \x - \xo 3:11 \xt Heb 2:4\x*Adudi houjik masi mayek sengle madudi Tengban Mapugi mangda mi kana amatabu Wayel Yathanggi mapanna chumhanbide. Maramdi Mapugi Puyana hai, “Thajabagi mapanna Tengban Mapuna chumhanbiraba mi adukhaktana hinggani.”
\v 12 \x - \xo 3:12 \xt Levi 18:5\x*Adubu Wayel Yathangdi thajabada yumpham oide. Madugi onnabada Mapugi Puyana asumna hai, “Wayel Yathangna haiba khudingmakpu touba mahak aduna hingjagani.”
\p 
\v 13 \x - \xo 3:13 \xt Aniwa 21:23\x*Adubu Christtana eikhoigidamak sirap oibiraduna Wayel Yathangna purakpa sirap adudagi eikhoibu handokpire; maramdi Mapugi Puyana hai, “Uthakta yanba mi pumnamak adu Tengban Mapugi sirap phanglabani.”
\v 14 Jisu Christtagi mapanna Tengban Mapuna Abraham-da wasakpikhiba yaipha thoujal adu atoppa phurupsingda pibinabagidamak Christtana masi toubikhibani. Masi thajabagi mapanna Tengban Mapuna wasakpikhiba Thawai adu eikhoina phangjanabagidamaktani.
\s1 Wayel yathang amasung wasakpiba
\p 
\v 15 Ichil-Inaosa, eikhoigi nungtigi punsida thokpa khudam ama eina pijage. Mi anina karigumba hiram amada yanakhrabadi aduga yannache innakhrabadi madu mi kana amatana thugaiba ngamde aduga maduda kari amata hapchinba ngamde.
\v 16 Aduga Tengban Mapuna mahakki wasaksing adu Abraham amasung mahakki chada-naodada pibikhi. Masida Mapugi Puyana “Chada-naodasingda” haibadi mi mayamda haikhide adubu “Chada-naodada” haibadi mi amatagi maramda haikhi, madu Christtani.
\v 17 \x - \xo 3:17 \xt Khong 12:40\x*Eina hairiba asi masini: Tengban Mapuna Abraham-da warepnaba ama pibikhi aduga madu ngakkani haina wasakpikhi. Aduga chahi chamari khunthragi matungda pikhiba Wayel Yathang aduna warepnaba adubu thugaiba ngamde aduga asumna wasak adubu kakthatpa ngamde.
\v 18 \x - \xo 3:18 \xt Rom 4:14\x*Maramdi Tengban Mapugi khudol adu Wayel Yathangda tangjaba oirabadi madu Tengban Mapugi wasakpibada tangjaba amuk oidre. Adumakpu Tengban Mapuna Abraham-da khudol adubu pikhiba adu mahakki wasak adugi maramnani.
\p 
\v 19 Adu oirabadi Wayel Yathang pinabiribasi karino? Madu ayol aral touba haibasi karino haiba utpinabagidamak hapchinbibani aduga madu wasakpikhiba Abraham-gi chada naoda aduna lenglaktribaphaobagini. Wayel Yathang adu taisinnabiba mi amada swarga dutsinggi khuthangda sinnakhi.
\v 20 Adumakpu taisinnabiba adu kangbu amakhakta oiba matamda mathou tade adubu Tengban Mapudi amakhaktani.
\s1 Wayel yathang pibagi maram
\p 
\v 21 Adu oirabadi Wayel Yathang asi Tengban Mapugi wasaksing adugi maiyoktara? Madu khak oidasanu! Maramdi hingba piba ngamba wayel yathang ama mioibana phanglamlabadi madu injaduna Tengban Mapuna makhoibu chumhanbiramgadabani.
\v 22 Adubu Mapugi Puyana hai madudi taibangpan apumba asi papki panggal makhada leire; aduga asumna Jisu Christtabu thajabada yumpham oiduna wasakpikhiba khudol adu thajabasing aduda pinabire.
\p 
\v 23 Adubu thajaba aduna laktringeigi mamangda, Wayel Yathang aduna eikhoi pumnamakpu lakkadouba thajaba adu phongdoktriba phaoba phadok oina phajinduna thamlammi.
\v 24 Maram aduna eikhoibu thajabagi mapanna chumhanbinaba Christtana lenglaktriphaoba Wayel Yathangna eikhoibu yengsinbibagi thougal toubasing adu oire.
\v 25 Adubu houjikti thajaba adu lakle, aduga eikhoi yengsinbiba adugi makhada leitre.
\p 
\v 26 Maram aduna thajabagi mapanna nakhoina Christta Jisuda amata oina punsinjaduna Tengban Mapugi machasing oijare.
\v 27 Maramdi Christtada baptize louraba nakhoi pumnamakna Christtabu phi setpagum setle.
\v 28 Maram aduna Jihudi nattraga Greek, minai nattraga ningtamba, nupa nattraga nupigi marakta khetnaba karisu leite; maramdi nakhoi pumnamak Christta Jisuda amatani.
\v 29 \x - \xo 3:29 \xt Rom 4:13\x*Nakhoina Christtagi oirabadi nakhoi Abraham-gi chada-naodasingni aduga wasakpibagi matung-inna nakhoi yumlep charasingni.
\c 4
\p 
\v 1 Eina haibadi yumlepchara aduna pumnamakki mapu oirabasu mahakna angang oiriba makheidi mahakna minai amaga khetnaba karisu leite.
\v 2 Yumlep chara adu mapa aduna lepkhiba matam adu youdriba phaobadi mahakpu sennabiriba mising amadi asin arang touriba mising adugi makha ponna lei.
\v 3 Matou adugumduna eikhoina thawaigi oina mapung phadringeigi mamangda eikhoisu taibangpan asigi thawaigi oiba pangalsing adugi minai oiduna leirammi.
\v 4 Adubu matam aduna pumsu surabada Tengban Mapuna mahakki Machanupabu thabirakle. Mahakna taibangda nupi amagi macha ama oina lenglakkhi aduga mahakna Jihudigi Wayel Yathanggi makha ponna leikhi.
\v 5 \x - \xo 4:5-7 \xt Rom 8:15-17\x*Madu eikhoina Tengban Mapugi machasing oiraknanaba Wayel Yathanggi makha ponna leirambasing adubu handokpinabani.
\p 
\v 6 Aduga nakhoi mahakki machasing oibagi maramna Tengban Mapuna mahakki Machanupagi Thawai adubu eikhoigi thamoinungda thabirakle aduga Thawai aduna “Abba, Ipa” haina koujei.
\v 7 Maram aduna nahak makha tana minai oidre adubu Tengban Mapugi macha oire. Aduga nahakna mahakki macha oirabanina mahakna machasinggidamak thambiriba pumnamak adu Tengban Mapuna nangonda pinabigani.
\s1 Paul-na Galatia-gi misinggidamak khanjaba
\p 
\v 8 Mamangda nakhoina Tengban Mapu khangdringei matamda, mahousana Tengban Mapu nattaba makhoising adugi minai oiduna leirammi.
\v 9 Adubu houjikti nakhoina Tengban Mapubu khangle aduga henna Tengban Mapunasu nakhoibu khangle. Aduga karamna nakhoina asonba amadi karisu kanadaba pangalsing aduda hanba pamlibano? Karigi nakhoina amuk hanna makhoising adugi minai oiba pamlibano?
\v 10 Nakhoina akhannaba numit, tha, kum-tha amadi chahi ngaktuna lei.
\v 11 Ei nakhoigidamak ki! Eina nakhoigidamak nomjakhiba thabak pumnamak adu arembada touba taragadra.
\p 
\v 12 Ichil inaosing eina nakhoida haijari, eigumna oibiyu maramdi eina nakhoigumna oirakle. Nakhoina eingonda aranba karisu toukhide.
\v 13 Eigi hakchangda anaba leibagi maramna eina ahanba oina nakhoida Aphaba Pao sandokkhi haibadu nakhoina khang-i.
\v 14 Adubu eigi hakchanggi phibham aduna nakhoida achouba changyeng oiraba phaobada nakhoina eibu hanthana khanbikhide aduga yadaba toukhide. Madugi mahutta Tengban mapugi swarga dut ama lousinbagum amadi Christta Jisu masamakpu lousinbagum nakhoina eibu lousinbikhi.
\v 15 Nakhoi adukki matik haraorammi! Adubu kari toukhrabage? Ei isana haiba ngamgani adudi nakhoina yarabadi nakhoigi namit adu phaoba kotthoktuna madu eingonda piramgani.
\v 16 Achumba asi nakhoida haibagidamak houjik ei nakhoigi yeknaba oirabra?
\p 
\v 17 Atoppa makhoising aduna nakhoida thawai yamna yaoba matou utli adubu makhoigi pandam adudi aphaba natte. Makhoina pamba haibabu makhoina nakhoida thawai yaojaba adugumna nakhoinasu makhoida chap manaba thawai yaoba adu leinanaba nakhoibu eikhoidagi tokhai tahanba aduni.
\v 18 Houjik, eina nakhoiga leiminnaringei matam asi khaktada nattaduna, aphaba maramgidamak oirabadi matam pumnamakta asigumba yamna thawai yaoba asi leiba phei.
\v 19 Eigi nungsijaraba angangsa! Amukkasu hanna, mamana angang unaba matamda phaoba cheina aduga chap manaba cheina adu nakhoida Christtagi sakwong adu semgattriba phaoba eina nakhoigidamak phaojari.
\v 20 Houjik eina nakhoiga loinana kayada leiminnajaningliba, aduga eigi wahei khonpham asi hongdokchaningba, maramdi eina nakhoigi maramda palleppham khangde.
\s1 Hagar amadi Sarah-gi pandam
\p 
\v 21 Wayel Yathanggi makha ponna leiningba nakhoida eina hangge: Wayel Yathangna kari haibage haibadu nakhoi tadabra?
\v 22 \x - \xo 4:22 \xt Meihou 16:15; 21:2\x*Maramdi masi iduna lei, madudi Abraham-gi macha ani lei, amana minai nupigi machani, aduga amana maningtambi nupigi machani.
\v 23 Minai nupina pokpa mahakki macha adudi hachanggi matung-inna pokpani aduga maningtambina pokpa mahakki macha aduna Tengban Mapugi wasakpiba adugi mahei oina pokpani.
\v 24 Hairibasing asi pandam oina haibani. Nupi ani asina utlibasi warepnaba anini. Macha adubu minai oina pokpa adu Hagarni, aduga mahakna Sinai chingda warepnakhiba warepnaba adu phongdokpibani.
\v 25 Hagarna Arabia-da leiba Sinai Ching adu utpani aduga houjik oiriba Jerusalem saharga pangkhakni, maramdi mahakna mahakki machasingga loinana minai oiri.
\v 26 Adubu swargagi oiba Jerusalem asidi maningtambini, aduga mahakti eikhoigi imani.
\v 27 \x - \xo 4:27 \xt Isa 54:1\x*Maramdi, Mapugi Puyana hai,
\q1 Haraojaro, he chaboktabi nupi, angang amata poktribi!
\q2 Haraobaga loinana lao amadi khonjel thokna lao, naoyek amukta phangdribi nahak.
\q1 Maramdi hundokpiramlabi nupigi machasing aduna
\q2 mapuroibana keidounungda thadoktabi nupi adugi machasingdagi masing yamgani.
\p 
\v 28 Ichil-inaosa, houjik nakhoi Isaac-na oikhibagumna, Tengban Mapuna wasakpikhiba adugi mahei oina phangjaba Tengban Mapugi machasingni.
\v 29 \x - \xo 4:29\xt Meihou 21:9\x*Matam aduda hakchanggi matung-inna pokkhiba macha aduna Tengban Mapugi Thawaigi matung-inna pokpa mahak adubu ot-neibikhi. Aduga maduga chap mannana houjiksu oiri.
\v 30 \x - \xo 4:30 \xt Meihou 21:10\x*Adubu Mapugi Puyana kari haibage? “Minai nupi amasung machanupa adu tanthokkhro, maramdi minai nupina pokpa macha aduna maning tambi nupina pokpa macha aduga mapagi lanthum adu saruk phangminnaroidabani.”
\v 31 Maram aduna, ichil-inaosa, eikhoi minai nupigi machasing natte adubu maning tambigi machasingni.
\c 5
\s1 Christtada ningtamba
\p 
\v 1 Christtana eikhoibu ningtamhankhiba adu eikhoina ningtamba oinabagidamaktani. Maram aduna chetna leppu aduga amuk hanna minaigi potpu adubu nasada thonggatchaganu.
\p 
\v 2 Tao, Paul eina nakhoida hairi madudi nakhoi un kakpada yajarabadi, Christtadi nakhoida kanaba suklei leitre.
\v 3 Un kakpada yajariba mi khudingda eina amukka hanna cheksin wa asi hairi madudi mahakna wayel yathang apumba inba tabani.
\v 4 Wayel yathang ngaktuna chumhanbinaba hotnariba nakhoi Christtadagi tokhaina tarabani; nakhoi Tengban Mapugi thoujalgi wangmada leirabani.
\v 5 Adubu, eikhoigidamaktadi, Tengban Mapuna eikhoibu mahakki mangda chumhanbigani haiba asina eikhoigi ashani; aduga Tengban Mapugi Thawaigi panggalgi mapanna eikhoigi thajabana eikhoina khourangna ngaijariba adu masini.
\v 6 Maramdi eikhoina Christta Jisuga amata oina punsinjaba matamda un kakpagi amadi kaktabagi khetnaba karisu leite. Maruoiriba adudi nungsibagi mapanna thabak touriba thajaba aduni.
\p 
\v 7 Nakhoina ningthina lamjel chelllammi! Achumba adu illamba adudagi kanana nakhoibu thingbage? Kamdouna mahakna nakhoibu themdokpage?
\v 8 Asigumba makhalgi themdokpa asi nakhoibu koubiba Tengban Mapudagi lakpa natte.
\v 9 \x - \xo 5:9 \xt 1 Cor 5:6\x*Hamei khajiktana atotpa yam matum apumba kamkhathalli.
\v 10 Adubu nakhoina atoppa wakhallon amata louroi haina eina Ibungoda thajei. Aduga nakhoibu chamamnahalliba mahak adu kana kana oirabasu Tengban Mapuna mahakpu cheirak pigani.
\p 
\v 11 Adubu ichil inaosa, eigi oinadi, un kakpa asi tangaiphadabani haina eina houjik phaoba sandoklabadi, karigi eibu houjik phaoba ot neibiribano? Aduga maduna achumba oiramlabadi eina cross-ki maramda sandokliba asina khudi thiba thokhallamloidabani.
\v 12 Nakhoibu pukning olhalliba makhoina un kakpadagi hendokna masa onhanjaramlabadi eina penjaramgadabani.
\p 
\v 13 Ichil inaosa, nakhoibu ningtamhannaba koubibani. Adubu nakhoigi naning tamba adu hakchanggi apamba adu thunghannabagi oina sijinnaganu. Madugi mahutta nungsibagi mapanna nakhoi amaga amaga thougal tounou.
\v 14 \x - \xo 5:14 \xt Levi 19:18\x*Maramdi wayel yathang apumba adu yathang amakhak asi ngakpana thunghallabani: “Nakhoina nakhoigi yumlon keironnababu nasamakum nungsiyu”
\v 15 Adubu nakhoina lamlakki sagumna amaga amaga chiknaduna chathoknarabadi, cheksillu nattrabadi amana amabu pummang manghalnaragani.
\s1 Thawai amadi hakchanggi thabaksing
\p 
\v 16 Aduna eina hairi, Thawaigi mapanna chatlu, adu oirabadi nakhoina hakchanggi apambasing adu thunghalloi.
\v 17 \x - \xo 5:17 \xt Rom 7:15-23\x*Maramdi hakchanggi apamba aduna thawaigi apamsing adugi maiyokta lei, aduga thawaigi apamba aduna hakchanggi oiba adugi maiyokta lei. Nakhoigi apamba adu nakhoina toudananaba makhoina amaga amaga yetnei.
\v 18 Nakhoibu Thawai aduna chingbirabadi, nakhoina wayel yathanggi makha pondre.
\p 
\v 19 Aduga hakchanggi thabaksing adudi mayek seng-i: nupa nupi lannaba, amotpa thabak, lamchat ludaba,
\v 20 lai murti latpa, hikap yaikappa, yengthinaba, mot tinnadaba, kalak khambannaba, mei houna saoba, marannai tanba, saona khatnaba, kanglup tannaba,
\v 21 khambanba, yu ngaoba, makhe langba, aduga masiga mannaba makhei asini. Eina mamangda haikhibagum cheksin wa asi nakhoida hairi: asigumba thabaksing asi touba makhoising aduna Tengban Mapugi leibak adu phangloi.
\p 
\v 22 Adubu thawaigi maheidi nungsiba, haraoba, ingthaba, khaangheiba, chanbiheiba, aphaba, thajaba yaba,
\v 23 pukning tappa, amadi masa khudum chanjabani. Hairibasing asigi maiyokta wayel yathang amata leite.
\v 24 Aduga Christta Jisugi oikhrabasing aduna hakchang adu madugi phattaba pukning ihulsing amasung apambasing pumnamakka loinana cross-ta hatkhre.
\v 25 Eikhoina Thawaigi mapanna hingbagi maramna, eikhoina thawaigi mapanna chatsu chatsi.
\v 26 Amaga amaga singnaduna amadi khambannaduna eikhoi napal tougumsi.
\c 6
\s1 Atoppagi potlum puminnaba
\p 
\v 1 Ichil inaosa, karigumba papta taba mi amabu pharabadi, thawaigi mapanna hingliba nakhoina ing-tappaga loinana mahakpu hannagi maphamda hanjinhanbiyu. Aduga nakhoi nasamakpusu athemba aduda tadanaba nasana cheksinjou.
\v 2 Nakhoi amana amagi potlum puminnou, matou asumna nakhoina Christtagi wayel yathang adu thunghallu.
\v 3 Kanagumbana karisu nattaba oiraga masabu karigumba amani haina khanjarabadi mahak masana masabu minamjarabani.
\v 4 Mi khudingmakna masa masagi thabak chang yengjasanu. Maduna aphaba oirabadi, kanagumba ateina touba aduga changdamnaba toudana mahak masana toujaba adugidamak chaothokchasanu.
\v 5 Maramdi nakhoi khudingna nasa nasagi potlum pujagadabani.
\p 
\v 6 Tengban Mapugi wa tamjaba phangjariba mahak aduna mahakki leijaba aphaba pot khudingmak mahakpu tambiriba oja aduga saruk phangminnasanu.
\p 
\v 7 Nasana nasabu minamhan-ganu; Tengban Mapubu noknaphade, maramdi mi amana hunkhi hunkhiba adumak mahakna lokkani.
\v 8 Maramdi masagi hakchangbu pelhannaba hunba mahak aduna hachangdagi amangba lokchagani; adubu Thawai adubu pelhannaba hunba mahak aduna Thawai adudagi lomba naidana hingba lokchagani.
\v 9 Maram aduna eikhoina aphaba toubada chokthagumsi; maramdi eikhoina chokthadrabadi achaba matamda eikhoina mahei lokkani.
\v 10 Maram aduna eikhoina khudongchaba phangba phangbada, mi pumnamakta aphaba tousi, thoidok hendokna thajaba ichil inaosinggi imung manungda aphaba tousi.
\s1 Aroiba cheksin wa amadi khurumjaba
\p 
\v 11 Yengbiyu, eigi ikhutmakna nakhoida kayada chaoba mayekna iriba!
\v 12 Nakhoibu namduna un kak-hannaba hotnariba makhoising adu hakchanggi mapanna misingbu pelhannaba hotnariba mising aduni. Christtagi cross-ki maramgidamak makhoibu ot-neidanaba khaktagidamak makhoina madu toubani.
\v 13 Un kaklaba makhoi aduna phaoba wayel yathang adu inde; adumakpu nakhoigi hakchangda un kakpa adugi maramda makhoina chaothokchanaba nakhoibu un kakpa adu makhoina pammi.
\v 14 Adubu eigidamaktadi eikhoigi Ibungo Jisu Christtagi cross-ki maramkhaktagidamak nattana keidounungda eina chaothoktasanu; maramdi Ibungogi cross-ki mapanna taibangpan asina eingonda aduga eina taibangpanda cross-ta sire.
\v 15 Un kakpa nattraga kaktaba haiba adu karisu natte; adubu maruoiba adudi anouba khutsem ama oibaduni.
\v 16 Pathap asibu illiba makhoising adugi mathakta amadi Tengban Mapugi oiba Israel-gi mathakta ingthaba amadi chanbiba oisanu.
\p 
\v 17 Houjiktagi houduna, kana amatana eingonda awaba pidasanu, maramdi eigi hakchangda leiriba dakpham asina eihak Ibungo Jisugi minai amani haiba utlabani.
\p 
\v 18 Ichil inaosa, eikhoigi Ibungo Jisu Christtagi thoujal aduna nakhoigi thawaiga loinabisanu. Amen.
